Comment: 10,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsuko Kagari, I am appointing you to hand wash all of the academy's laundry.
Comment: 10,0:06:20.76,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Sorcerer's Stone,\Nnone of the fairies can move. {I'm not sure about calling all the goblins and stuff fairies. also it's a different word than faerie last episode}
Comment: 10,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why are Lotte and me even helping you with your punishment?
