Comment: 10,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You have only yourselves to blame for pushing magic as it falls out of favor.
Comment: 10,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making immense profits from my online investments.
