Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugar,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,spice,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be... pickled plums! {these were the ingredients chosen to create the perfect little witch}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.09,0:01:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's mix!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Another batch of ingredients wasted.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It only gets messed up because of all the extra stuff you put in. {mmm, she's not really being nice here}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I might as well make it taste good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Constanze.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not witch-like at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This coming from you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Want one? They're light and fluffy. {what the hell is fuwa fuwa flavor. is this k-on?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.94,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Jasminka. Can't you take this more seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares as long as it gets done?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.17,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, anything you touch is guaranteed to fail.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it's pointless for a dunce to act so gung-ho. {it may be the jisho definition, but I like dunce because of the school connotations}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even ride a broom.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the dunce here, Amanda!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.75,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stuff it. Quit yapping into my ear.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just gave you a little lesson in manners. {yeah, this is better, and it's a set phrase}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you even know the first thing about manners!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}you're{\i0} just sore about losing the race!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I am not!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are green with envy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could possibly be jealous of a dunce like you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you're the dunce here!{## uh i guess you can undo some of the italics}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest dunce...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(801.143,685)}Is you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.74,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,685)}It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's definitely you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.07,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Scrylla!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yera Retoure!{I felt good about the last one, but this is harder. IeRARITO-RA. the first ie sound is a small soft "e"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was incredible, Diana!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genius witch!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.73,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, would it trouble you not to disturb the lesson with your vulgar feud?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are being quite the nuisance.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who're you calling vulgar?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to me that you're looking for some punishment.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.94,0:03:43.78,Default,,10,10,0,,A punishment that will drain the blood from your veins! {my blood is pumpin//I'm ready to fight when you are}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not use your time sitting in the corner to settle this matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The question of which of you is the biggest dunce in school.{## this... is okay, isn't?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana's such a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because she's a little good at magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.47,0:04:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn what family she's from.\NThat snobby attitude just pisses me off! {had condescending before}{## i'd like to replace this "attitude" in the light of my earlier edits, but this is kinda the best word to use here; oh well}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your "genius witch" and stuff it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.93,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why am I the only one here\Ntaking the cleaning seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get closer!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.77,0:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorcerer's Stone was stolen!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, Kagari-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole bunch{flight} of dragons came and flew away with it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the oracle was correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The dragon's wrath...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrath?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What wrath?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. We are already aware of the situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go get the Sorcerer's Stone back right away! We'll lend you our help too! {sup >>153114150, I saw you read these}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... "we"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That will not do, and that goes double for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.23,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We will resolve this issue,\Nso you two return to your rooms.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorcerer's Stone is the source of our magic!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to use magic at Luna Nova\Nwithout it, and it doesn't look like you care!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is enough, Akko and Amanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.65,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we had assigned you to cleaning duty as punishment.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This isn't the time—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsuko Kagari, I am appointing you to handwash all of the academy's laundry.{## going with longman DCE here}{it's on you then}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for you too, Amanda O'Neill!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, step to it! On the double!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to do the laundry?!{## ... legwashing?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.{## holy shit jasminka do something worthwhile; also fuck yeah, this TL got burned way too often}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.76,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Sorcerer's Stone,\Nnone of the sprites can move. {I'm not sure about calling all the goblins and stuff fairies. also it's a different word than faerie last episode}{## i think sprite might actually be a bit better here, you could probably argue that fairies/goblins/stuff are subsets of sprites}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.13,0:06:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other option than for us to do the cleaning, laundry, and cooking.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why are Lotte and I even helping you with your punishment?{## sucy can use the correct form i'd say}{I just wasn't sure}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Why are we wasting our time doing all this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.31,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill out with the pedaling, you're splashing water all the way over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying we can even do against the dragons?{## tfw discourse markers}{this works too}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the hags were shaking in their bloomers.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.33,0:06:52.76,Default,,10,10,0,,Well, legend says that dragons used to slice witches open\Nand slurp out their blood for magic replenishment.{## there's better ways to extract mana, just saying}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'd eat them, meat and bone.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.26,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross. But I doubt there are any witch-eating dragons around these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.39,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that mean that instead of witches, they stole \Nthe Sorcerer's Stone to replenish their magic?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but who knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.93,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The first dragon from around here that comes to mind is the one from the Rastaban Ruins.{## the transition should be sufficiently smooth while still not misrepresenting the original line (too much), i hope}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, you know it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, it was known as\None of the more brutal dragons.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But hardly anyone has seen it in the last hundred years or so.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you for rising from your hundred-year break!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.54,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for stealing our precious Sorcerer's Stone at the exact time we're here in school!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.68,Default,,10,10,0,,You've left us no choice but to take back the Stone ourselves!{## covering the mouth is okay here if we fuck around with the margins and make it a one-liner}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And right on cue, there's another one of Akko's crazy ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.96,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.41,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you should be concerning yourselves with is the laundry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do refrain from taking any futile actions.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you come here for?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Professor Finneran to relay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.92,0:07:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've finished the laundry,\Nyou are to draw water.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not even close to being done with the laundry though.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This affects you too, Diana!{## ayyyyy}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.26,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Sorcerer's Stone,\Nthere won't be any more classes!{## "from tomorrow"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even use any magic.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.25,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make your plan to confront the dragon yourselves any more likely to succeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what'll happen unless we try!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell already.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.49,0:08:24.02,Default,,10,10,0,,People like you, who cannot even keep up in class, would only compound the problem if they were to interfere.{## i basically needed to add the commas; i'm a firm believer in correct handling of appositions}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.02,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it is far too often that you act without proper thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.82,0:08:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it not benefit us all for you to recognize your habit of troubling everyone involved with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.48,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If this goes on unchanged, then one day even your friends will grow unwilling to put up with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you care? Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is fool around.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.99,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack goals, but please don't use that as an excuse to inconvenience those around you.{## might be too gimmicky, please feel free to use "those around you"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.74,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've relayed the message.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.31,0:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks for telling us. G-Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko.{## sad akko still makes me ;_;}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.60,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not just gonna let her lay into us\Nand keep quiet about it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.07,0:09:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hold on you two, don't tell me you were serious!{## bakakko and bakamanda}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no stopping Akko once she's like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But there's still laundry...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What about the water?{## FINALLY}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The dragon hunting squad is ready to rock!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.91,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Due to the sprites' current inability to perform their cleaning, laundry, and cooking duties,{## apostrophe was missing anyway}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have assigned students to each.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.28,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to report to the headmistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's currently away from campus.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At a time like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.{## holy shit such authority, diana is the best}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, how rare.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These characters...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our magic's starting to fill up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be getting close to the Sorcerer's Stone.{## "closer"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I think that's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rastaban Ruins.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.88,0:11:00.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(605,605)\fnGriffin\c&H1A1A23&\3c&H000000&\fs60\blur0.5\pos(1012,69)}Little Witch Academia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:11:00.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(605,605)\fnGriffin\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs60\blur0.5\pos(1012,69)\1a&HFF&\t(0,605,\1a&H00&)\t(4525,5130,\1a&HFF&)}Little Witch Academia
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no question, those are the Rastaban Ruins.{## looks like an average english town tbh}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the ones who stole the Sorcerer's Stone!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got incoming!{## should work}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Let's split into groups!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here! Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Slonhon Deance! {the -hon Deance is the same as the training wheels spell cast in ep3}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Got them!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte! Sucy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Constanze! Jasna! {okay, let me explain. this is ヤースナ, which in Russian is ясно. it's actually a real word that means "clear" or "understood". It appears that Amanda is using it as a nickname for Jasminka for some reason here}{## okay her name is all sorts of non-standard especially considering the kana for her full name, but we can assume jasna is the quasi-official nickname of jasminenka (technically yasminenka?), much lika mari*a is shortened to masha and alexander is shortened to sasha etc; yasmin* is rather unusual for eastern slavic regions but fairly common in south slavic languages especially with a muslim minority or majority, i.e. bosnia or bulgaria}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, after them!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.10,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this underneath the ruins?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we made it in somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of room is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a kitchen storage room.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna tell me it actually eats witches, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.27,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your claws off them!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you planning to eat me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't taste good at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a stomachache!{## i assume you dislike the looks of it but... it's better this way}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, definitely, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't eat me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.86,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in their right mind would eat a witch? Not to mention one who looks as rancid as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How rude! I'm deliciou—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Got'cha.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.51,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume you're the ones who got caught by my security system.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a food processor?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're Luna Nova students.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.30,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the money you owe me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The money we owe?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Headmistress Holbrooke send it with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.23,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? We just came to take back the Sorcerer's Stone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for bothering you this late. {eh, she doesn't really say anything here, just pleasantries}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Headmistress?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are. Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.54,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls... what in the world are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.98,0:16:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Were these students a ploy to buy you some time, Headmistress?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.82,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not, Lord Fafnir! {not sure what kind of titles dragons usually get}{## i don't know a single dragon personally so i wouldn't know, but since there's only one fafnir in norse mythology and that fafnir is of noble blood, this should be okay}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you brought my money?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept these instead...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.95,0:16:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a heap of junk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not think you can wriggle your way out of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What I demand is cold, hard cash!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you explain what this whole money thing's about already?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ransom for the Sorcerer's Stone?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.96,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna Nova has an enormous amount \Nof debt, and it's owed to yours truly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't received a single interest payment on it over the last year.{## my biggest gripes with this episode's editing: annuity would be the correct term, but this is a children's cartoon. still makes me uncomfortable af; also fixed the timing}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one penny!{## aka pls this is somerset, not idaho}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I call, all I get are excuses.{## i'd prefer the past tense here}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.76,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you that I'd take your Sorcerer's Stone the next time you ignore me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We never thought you would make good on your threat...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, the Sorcerer's Stone...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.65,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Was repossessed because the school defaulted.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.04,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider it a warning. Even selling it wouldn't cover a fraction of the debt you owe.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How the heck much did we borrow?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Fafnir, we beg your understanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna Nova is losing more students each year.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.74,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We are barely receiving one-tenth the number of applicants as we were during the golden age of magic.{## that kinda makes me sad; also consider using caps on the golden age, though it looks kinda iffy and forced}{not necesarily a time period though I do understand}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You have only yourselves to blame for pushing magic while it's falling out of favor.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My online investments are netting me immense profits.{## haha fuck, this is hilarious}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.12,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you are so well off, then please have mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.71,0:17:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to wait another second!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.62,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will repossess Luna Nova and sell it off myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna Nova has finally reached its end...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you grumpy old dragon!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Old?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that giant heart you have just for show?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you need the money. Don't be a stickler!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And since you're a dragon and all, what's even the point of making all that money?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with a dragon making money?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.63,0:18:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Money doesn't discriminate between humans and dragons.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.86,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna Nova is reaching the end of its usefulness anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.62,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to collect on it before its value drops to nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! No way in hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my own ambitions! \NI won't let you shut down Luna Nova! {maybe she should take up a card gam—OH WAIT}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better care about what I want! Stingy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling stingy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You stingy dragon!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You return what you borrow. That's how the real world works.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking everything that you owe me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe you exactly nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.19,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the promissory note you signed with Luna Nova one thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Promissory note"?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a promissory note?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's written in ancient Dragonese, so nobody could read it. {sounds good to me, or we could use Old[e] Dragonese}{## this should be good, makes most sense linguistically; i was thinking of Dragontongue but we shouldn't inject too much}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.11,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can, Diana?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I became fluent at the age of twelve.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mention of interest anywhere on this.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there was never a need to pay interest in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.34,0:19:20.30,Default,,10,10,0,,You abused the fact that our teachers could not read ancient Dragonese and pulled the wool over their eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You had them pay nonexistent interest!{## they did pay interest in the past?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.14,0:19:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A baseless accusation. There's no such thing\Nas a non-interest-bearing loan these days.{## let's go full technical}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.22,0:19:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I declare a contract that old invalid!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.00,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are we to understand that the debt itself is also invalidated?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.18,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,According to my calculations,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.18,0:19:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the sum of the payments made by Luna Nova far exceeds the principal sum of the initial debt.{## this should be fully correct without going over the top with technicalities, also "amount of capital" does not apply here; tfw writing a final thesis in a finance topic}{just you wait, one day we'll sub an anime about neuroscience}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.73,0:19:57.96,Default,,10,10,0,,Considering that the interest itself has been invalidated,\Nmay we assume the rest of the debt to be cleared?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.35,0:20:03.80,Default,,10,10,0,,Regarding the refunding of the overpayments, we will provide you with the proper documentation at a later date.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.93,0:20:13.90,Default,,10,10,0,,In light of these arguments, we request the immediate return of our Sorcerer's Stone, {\i1}Mister{\i0} Fafnir.{## wanna italicize the "mister" to make it clear she's on the same level as him, unlike the headmistress?; good mic drop opportunity}{sure why not}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.89,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.89,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was the end...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.56,0:20:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has no need for dragons or witches in this age of science.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.24,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is fated to be forgotten in the near future.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.39,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, magic has the power to move hearts!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.46,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been quite some time since I've last heard someone spout a line that naive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.43,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch! I'm gonna become an amazing witch one day and make the whole world gasp in surprise!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Is that the dream you were talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.66,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn soon enough that no man can live off dreams alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.88,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Gramps! Try and keep your greed in check.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.03,0:21:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that there were still humans\Nwith that look in their eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, we're back to laundry duty.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.40,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect? We broke the rules\Nand left campus without permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.91,0:21:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful this is the end of our punishment.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.91,0:21:57.17,Default,,10,10,0,,Yeah, but it still sucks that Diana totally stole the show.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how perfect can one girl be?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so perfect I wanna hurl.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what makes her worth taking down!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no qualms with her as my rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.96,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're nowhere near good enough for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your place as the school's biggest dunce.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.89,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest dunce here is{\i1} you{\i0}, Amanda!{## heh, for good measure}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}you{\i0}, Akko!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.41,0:22:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.21,0:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just stop it already, you two!
